Ferry Street, north side, west from and including Jacob, to and including Gold Streets. Shown at the termination of Ferry Street, is No. 87 Gold Street, north of the N.W. corner of Spruce Street.

March 26, 1931.

P. L. Sperr.

(1)

March 26, 1931.

P. L. Sperr.

A portion of the same, showing a close view of Nos. 11-17, 19-23 and No. 63 Frankfort Street (the 5-story corner house).
